<title>UK: Siebe posts offer for Whessoe.</title>
<headline>Siebe posts offer for Whessoe.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-02-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>British-based controls and engineering group Siebe Plc said on Friday it had posted its offer document for an agreed 46 million stg bid for instrumentation and controls firm Whessoe Plc.</p>
<p>The first closing date for the offer is March 13. SBC Warburg is acting for Siebe while Schroders acts for Whessoe.</p>
